text: Fyodorovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Ikryaninsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 682 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km SSW from Ikryanoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ikryaninsky District
title: Fyodorovka, Ikryaninsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
